274
0:11:34.26,000 --> 0:11:36,000
This is perhaps a first element

275
0:11:36.26,000 --> 0:11:38,000
of a change.

276
0:11:38.26,000 --> 0:11:4,000
In the future, I believe,

277
0:11:40.26,000 --> 0:11:43,000
we should draw examples from these different illustrations,

278
0:11:43.26,000 --> 0:11:45,000
not to have diplomacy

279
0:11:45.26,000 --> 0:11:48,000
