0:12:19.26,000 --> 0:12:21,000
along a broad mobilization.

293
0:12:21.26,000 --> 0:12:24,000
It's crucial to understand, I believe,

294
0:12:24.26,000 --> 0:12:26,000
because of technology and because of globalization,

