309
0:13:02.26,000 --> 0:13:04,000
as many means of communication,

310
0:13:04.26,000 --> 0:13:07,000
means of being connected, means of reaching out,

311
0:13:07.26,000 --> 0:13:09,000
means of including.

312
0:13:09.26,000 --> 0:13:11,000
The diplomatic toolbox

313
0:13:11.26,000 --> 0:13:14,000
is actually full of different tools we can use

314
0:13:14.26,000 --> 0:13:16,000
to strengthen our communication.

315
0:13:16.26,000 --> 0:13:19,000
But the problem is that we are coming out of a decade

316
0:13:19.26,000 --> 0:13:21,000
